name: Guinso.GitHub.io
body:
### Welcome to Guinso GitHub
This is my personal project. Feel free to visit my repositories :)

***
[Kx-Doc](https://github.com/guinso/kx-doc)
This is a long term dynamic cross platform document project


***
[Hx-Core](https://github.com/guinso/hx-core)
My first experimental PHP utility libraries to build RESTful web server

[Hx-Http](https://github.com/guinso/hx-http)
Http I/O PHP library (extracted and refined from Hx-Core)

[Hx-Route](https://github.com/guinso/hx-route)
Http route utility PHP library (extracted and refined from Hx-Core)

[Hx-Db](https://github.com/guinso/hx-db)
RDBMS utility PHP library (extracted and refined from Hx-Core)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
